title: Sim City 4 - BAT Update - "Night Light Fix"
description:
** Patch *** Sim City 4 *** PC ***


This is a patch for SimCity 4 which cannot be downloaded from the official site without an unused serial number. 

It fixes the night-lighting issues that occur with user-created buildings and lots.

If you don&#039;t have a serial number for whatever reason, download this patch. Otherwise getting a hold of it will be extremely difficult.
